\c 8
\s Abahamba loEzra
\p
\v 1 Laba-ke zinhloko zaboyise, lombhalo wosendo lwabo abenyuka lami besuka eBhabhiloni ekubuseni kukaAthakisekisi inkosi.
\v 2 Kumadodana kaPhinehasi: UGerishomu\x + 1 Lan. 24.3,4.\x*. Kumadodana kaIthamari\x + 1 Lan. 24.3,4.\x*: UDaniyeli\x + Neh. 10.6.\x*. Kumadodana kaDavida: UHathushi\x + 1 Lan. 3.22. Neh. 10.4. 12.2.\x*.
\v 3 Kumadodana kaShekaniya\x + 1 Lan. 3.21.\x*, kumadodana kaParoshi\x + 2.3.\x*: UZekhariya, njalo kanye laye kwabhalwa ngombhalo wosendo, kwabesilisa, ikhulu lamatshumi amahlanu.
\v 4 Kumadodana kaPahathi-Mowabi: UEliyowenayi, indodana kaZerahiya, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamakhulu amabili\x + 2.6.\x*.
\v 5 Kumadodana kaShekaniya: Indodana kaJahaziyeli, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamakhulu amathathu\x + 1 Lan. 3.21.\x*.
\v 6 Njalo kumadodana kaAdini: UEbedi indodana kaJonathani, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamatshumi amahlanu\x + 2.15.\x*.
\v 7 Lakumadodana kaElamu: UJeshaya indodana kaAthaliya, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + 2.7.\x*.
\v 8 Lakumadodana kaShefathiya: UZebhadiya indodana kaMikayeli, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamatshumi ayisificaminwembili\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 9 Kumadodana kaJowabi: UObhadiya indodana kaJehiyeli, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamakhulu amabili letshumi lesificaminwembili\x + 2.6.\x*.
\v 10 Lakumadodana kaShelomithi: Indodana kaJosifiya, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abalikhulu lamatshumi ayisithupha.
\v 11 Lakumadodana kaBebayi: UZekhariya indodana kaBebayi, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abangamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili\x + 2.11,12. 10.28. Neh. 10.15.\x*.
\v 12 Lakumadodana kaAzigadi: UJohanani indodana kaHakatani, njalo kanye laye abesilisa abalikhulu letshumi\x + 2.11,12. 10.28. Neh. 10.15.\x*.
\v 13 Lakumadodana okucina kaAdonikamu, omabizo abo yila: OElifeleti, uJehiyeli, loShemaya, njalo kanye labo abesilisa abangamatshumi ayisithupha\x + 2.13.\x*.
\v 14 Lakumadodana kaBigivayi: OUthayi loZabudi, njalo kanye labo abesilisa abangamatshumi ayisikhombisa\x + 2.2,14.\x*.
\p
\v 15 Ngasengibabuthanisa ngasemfuleni oya eAhava\x + 8.21,31.\x*, samisa inkamba khona insuku ezintathu. Ngananzelela abantu labapristi, njalo kangitholanga lapho abamadodana kaLevi\x + 7.7.\x*.
\v 16 Ngasengithuma kuEliyezeri, kuAriyeli, kuShemaya, lakuElinathani, lakuJaribi, lakuElinathani, lakuNathani, lakuZekhariya\x + 8.3,11. Neh. 8.4. 12.41.\x*, lakuMeshulamu, izinhloko, lakuJoyaribi, lakuElinathani, abaqedisisayo\x + 10.15. Neh. 3.4,30. 6.18. 8.4. 10.7,20. 12.33.\x*,
\v 17 ngasengibalayela kuIdo, inhloko endaweni iKasifiya, ngafaka amazwi emlonyeni wabo ukuthi bathi kuIdo, \add l\add*abafowabo, amaNethini endaweni iKasifiya, ukuthi basilethele izikhonzi zendlu kaNkulunkulu wethu.
\v 18 Basebesilethela ngokwesandla esihle sikaNkulunkulu wethu phezu kwethu umuntu oqedisisayo\x + 7.6.\x* emadodaneni kaMahli indodana kaLevi indodana kaIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 6.19.\x*; loSherebiya lamadodana akhe labafowabo, itshumi lesificaminwembili\x + 8.24. Neh. 8.7. 9.4,5. 10.12. 12.24. Neh. 12.8.\x*;
\v 19 loHashabhiya\x + 8.24. Neh. 3.17. 10.11. 12.24.\x*, njalo kanye laye uJeshaya emadodaneni kaMerari, abafowabo lamadodana abo, amatshumi amabili\x + 1 Lan. 6.1,16.\x*;
\v 20 lakumaNethini\x + 7.7. 1 Lan. 9.2.\x*, uDavida leziphathamandla ababewanikele emsebenzini wamaLevi, amaNethini angamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amabili, wonke awo abizwa ngamabizo\x + Nani 1.17.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Ngasengimemezela ukuzila ukudla khona\x + 2 Lan. 20.3.\x* emfuleni iAhava\x + 8.21,31.\x* ukuze sizithobe phambi kukaNkulunkulu wethu\x + Levi 16.29.\x*, sizidingele kuye indlela eqondileyo thina labantwanyana bethu lazo zonke impahla zethu\x + Hlab. 5.8.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ngaba lenhloni ukucela enkosini ibutho labagadi bamabhiza ukusinceda ezitheni endleleni; ngoba sasiyitshelile inkosi sisithi: Isandla sikaNkulunkulu wethu siphezu kwabo bonke\x + 7.6.\x* abamdinga kube okuhle\x + Roma 8.28.\x*, kodwa amandla akhe lolaka lwakhe kuphezu kwabo bonke abamdelayo\x + Josh. 24.20. 2 Lan. 15.2.\x*.
\v 23 Ngakho sazila ukudla sadinga kuNkulunkulu wethu ngenxa yalokhu; wasencengeka ngathi\x + Gen. 25.21. Isa. 19.22.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Ngasengisehlukanisa abalitshumi lambili kunhloko zabapristi, oSherebiya\x + 8.18.\x*, uHashabhiya, labalitshumi kubafowabo kanye labo\x + 8.19.\x*.
\v 25 Ngasengibalinganisela isiliva legolide lezitsha\x + 7.15,16.\x*, umnikelo wendlu kaNkulunkulu wethu\x + Eks. 25.2.\x*, inkosi labacebisi bayo leziphathamandla zayo loIsrayeli wonke owayekhona ababekunikele\x + Hlu. 20.48.\x*;
\v 26 ngasengilinganisa esandleni sabo \w amathalenta\w** esiliva angamakhulu ayisithupha lamatshumi amahlanu, lamathalenta alikhulu ezitsha zesiliva, lamathalenta egolide alikhulu,
\v 27 lemiganu yegolide engamatshumi amabili\x + 1.10.\x* kuze kube zinhlamvu eziyinkulungwane, lezitsha ezimbili zethusi elikhazimulayo elihle eliloyiseka njengegolide\x + 1 Lan. 29.7.\x*.
\v 28 Ngasengisithi kibo: Lingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Levi 21.6.\x*, lezitsha zingcwele\x + Levi 22.2,3.\x*; lesiliva legolide kungumnikelo wesihle eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, uNkulunkulu wabobaba\x + 7.15,16.\x*.
\v 29 Kulondolozeni likugcine lize likulinganise phambi kwenduna yabapristi lamaLevi lenhloko zaboyise bakoIsrayeli eJerusalema, emakamelweni endlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 10.6. 2 Kho. 23.11.\x*\nd*.
\v 30 Abapristi lamaLevi basebesemukela isisindo sesiliva legolide lezitsha, ukuze bakuse eJerusalema, endlini kaNkulunkulu wethu.
\p
\v 31 Sasuka-ke emfuleni iAhava\x + 8.15,21.\x* ngolwetshumi lambili lwenyanga yokuqala ukuya eJerusalema\x + 7.9.\x*. Lesandla sikaNkulunkulu wethu sasiphezu kwethu, wasikhulula esandleni sesitha lomcathami endleleni\x + 7.6.\x*.
\v 32 Safika-ke eJerusalema, sahlala khona insuku ezintathu\x + Neh. 2.11.\x*.
\p
\v 33 Kwathi ngosuku lwesine isiliva legolide lezitsha kwalinganiswa endlini kaNkulunkulu wethu\x + 8.26,30.\x* ngesandla sikaMeremothi\x + Neh. 3.4,21. 10.5.\x* indodana kaUriya umpristi\x + Neh. 3.4,21. 8.4.\x*, njalo kanye laye uEleyazare indodana kaPhinehasi, njalo kanye labo oJozabadi indodana kaJeshuwa\x + 10.23. Neh. 8.7. 11.16.\x*, loNowadiya indodana kaBinuwi, amaLevi\x + 2.10. Neh. 3.24. 10.9.\x*,
\v 34 ngenani ngesisindo sakho konke; laso sonke isisindo sabhalwa ngalesosikhathi.
\v 35 Abantwana bokuthunjwa ababebuyile ekuthunjweni banikela iminikelo yokutshiswa kuNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli\x + 2.1.\x*, amajongosi alitshumi lambili ngenxa kaIsrayeli wonke, izinqama ezingamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye lesithupha, amawundlu angamatshumi ayisikhombisa lesikhombisa, izimpongo ezilitshumi lambili zaba ngumnikelo wesono; konke kwakungumnikelo wokutshiswa eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 6.17. 2 Lan. 29.21.\x*.
\p
\v 36 Basebenika imithetho yenkosi\x + 7.21.\x* kuziphathamandla zenkosi\x + Esta 3.12. 8.9. 9.3. Dan. 3.2,3,27. 6.2, 3.\x* lakubabusi\x + 1 Kho. 10.15. Neh. 2.7,9. 3.7.\x* nganeno komfula; basekela abantu lendlu kaNkulunkulu\x + 1.4.\x*.
